         <div xml:id="alalal-j36847"><!-- l4d48a8 -->
            <head xml:id="alalal-j36847-Hd1e99">Articulus 8</head>
            <head xml:id="alalal-j36847-Hd1e101" type="question-title">An lux solis erit major post judicium,
quam fuit ante?</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-j36847-d1e104">
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="13"/>ARTICULUS VIII.
<lb ed="#Bf" n="14"/>An lux solis erit major post judicium,
<lb ed="#Bf" n="15"/>quam fuit ante?
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-j36847-d1e113">
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="16"/>Deinde quaeritur de hoc quod dicit, E,
<lb ed="#Bf" n="17"/>paulo ante medium: <quote xml:id="alalal-j36847-Qd1e119"> Lé lux solis erit
<lb ed="#Bf" n="18"/>septempliciter, etc. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-j36847-d1e125">
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="19"/>Videtur enim hoc esse contra 
ratio<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="20"/>nem : quia lux solis data est ad mové
n<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="21"/>dum ad generationem inferiorum: ergo
<lb ed="#Bf" n="22"/>sublata generatione, debet auferri ejus
<lb ed="#Bf" n="23"/>lumen: non ergo debet tunc amplius 
lu<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="24"/>cere, sed minus.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-j36847-d1e142">
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="25"/>Ad hoc dicunt, quod remuncrabitur
<lb ed="#Bf" n="26"/>sol propter hominis dignitatem, ad cujus
<lb ed="#Bf" n="27"/>generationem movit, ut numerus 
clecto<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="28"/>rum impleretur,
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-j36847-d1e153">
               <lb ed="#Bf" n="29"/>Ad ovsecrum autem dicunt, quod lux
<lb ed="#Bf" n="30"/>non movebit amplius ad generationem,
<lb ed="#Bf" n="31"/>sed stabit: quia per motum causabat 
ge<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="32"/>nerationem. Dicunt autem, quod sol in
<lb ed="#Bf" n="33"/>sex primis diebus ante peccatum hominis
<lb ed="#Bf" n="34"/>plusquam modo luxit, et tunc redibit ad
<lb ed="#Bf" n="35"/>illam lucem, et insuper septies addetur
<lb ed="#Bf" n="36"/>ei tantum de lumine, quantum habuit in
<lb ed="#Bf" n="37"/>sex primis diebus. Homines autem in
<lb ed="#Bf" n="38"/>septuplum plusquam sol in illis diebus,
<lb ed="#Bf" n="39"/>scilicet post judicium, Et quid de hoc 
ve<lb break="no" ed="#Bf" n="40"/>rum sit, nullus scit nisi Deus.
</p>
         </div>
